# Staff — Internal Auth-Flow Endpoints
# UC-022: BFF resolves which tenants a Google account belongs to (staff login — returns array)
# UC-022 email fallback: when by-oauth returns nothing (Google account never linked), the BFF
# falls back to by-email-all to find and link any active, not-yet-linked staff record by email
# UC-025: BFF links Google account to an already-active staff record on first login
#
# Management endpoints (list, getById, invite, deactivate) have moved to staff.http
#
# Prerequisites:
#   1. pnpm infra:up           (start PostgreSQL + Pub/Sub emulator)
#   2. pnpm --filter @ikaro/backend run migration:run
#   3. pnpm --filter @ikaro/backend run dev
#
# REST Client environment: select "local" in VS Code status bar

@baseUrl     = {{backendUrl}}
@internalKey = {{$dotenv INTERNAL_API_KEY}}
@sub         = google-sub-admin-a
@staffId     = {{managerId}}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HAPPY PATH — by-oauth (UC-022)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get all staff records for a known Google OAuth ID (returns array — empty if none)
GET {{baseUrl}}/internal/staff/by-oauth?googleOAuthId={{sub}}
X-Internal-Key: {{internalKey}}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HAPPY PATH — by-email (UC-025 first-login lookup)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### Find staff by email + tenantId (returns 404 if not found)
GET {{baseUrl}}/internal/staff/by-email?email=gerente@lavacar.com.br&tenantId={{tenantId}}
X-Internal-Key: {{internalKey}}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HAPPY PATH — by-email-all (UC-022 generic-login email fallback, no tenant required)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### Find all staff records for an email across every tenant (returns array — empty if none).
### Used by the BFF's generic staff login when a Google account has never been linked to any
### staff record by OAuth ID — matches by Google's verified email instead.
GET {{baseUrl}}/internal/staff/by-email-all?email=gerente@lavacar.com.br
X-Internal-Key: {{internalKey}}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HAPPY PATH — link-google (UC-025)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### Link Google account to an active staff record (first login via invite link)
POST {{baseUrl}}/internal/staff/{{staffId}}/link-google
X-Internal-Key: {{internalKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenantId": "{{tenantId}}",
  "googleOAuthId": "{{sub}}",
  "email": "gerente@lavacar.com.br",
  "name": "Gerente Silva"
}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ERROR CASES
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### 401 — Missing X-Internal-Key (global guard)
GET {{baseUrl}}/internal/staff/by-oauth?googleOAuthId={{sub}}

###

### 400 — Missing googleOAuthId query parameter
GET {{baseUrl}}/internal/staff/by-oauth
X-Internal-Key: {{internalKey}}

###

### 400 — Missing email or tenantId for by-email
GET {{baseUrl}}/internal/staff/by-email?tenantId={{tenantId}}
X-Internal-Key: {{internalKey}}

###

### Empty array — Google account not registered as staff (200 [] instead of 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/internal/staff/by-oauth?googleOAuthId=unknown-sub-not-staff
X-Internal-Key: {{internalKey}}

###

### 404 — No staff with that email in this tenant
GET {{baseUrl}}/internal/staff/by-email?email=nobody@lavacar.com.br&tenantId={{tenantId}}
X-Internal-Key: {{internalKey}}

###

### 400 — Missing email query parameter for by-email-all
GET {{baseUrl}}/internal/staff/by-email-all
X-Internal-Key: {{internalKey}}

###

### Empty array — no staff with that email at any tenant (200 [] instead of 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/internal/staff/by-email-all?email=nobody@lavacar.com.br
X-Internal-Key: {{internalKey}}

###

### 404 — staffId not found in tenant
POST {{baseUrl}}/internal/staff/00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000009999/link-google
X-Internal-Key: {{internalKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenantId": "{{tenantId}}",
  "googleOAuthId": "{{sub}}",
  "email": "gerente@lavacar.com.br",
  "name": "Staff User"
}

###

### 403 — Staff account is deactivated
# Prerequisite chain: invite a throwaway staff member, then deactivate it,
# so this request has a genuinely deactivated record to call link-google against.

# @name inviteThrowawayStaff
POST {{baseUrl}}/staff/invite
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

{
  "email": "desativado-link-google@lavacar.com.br",
  "firstName": "Desativado",
  "lastName": "Teste",
  "role": "STAFF"
}

###

PATCH {{baseUrl}}/staff/{{inviteThrowawayStaff.response.body.staffId}}/deactivate
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

###

POST {{baseUrl}}/internal/staff/{{inviteThrowawayStaff.response.body.staffId}}/link-google
X-Internal-Key: {{internalKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenantId": "{{tenantId}}",
  "googleOAuthId": "{{sub}}",
  "email": "desativado-link-google@lavacar.com.br",
  "name": "Desativado Teste"
}

###

### 422 — Google email does not match invited email
POST {{baseUrl}}/internal/staff/{{staffId}}/link-google
X-Internal-Key: {{internalKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenantId": "{{tenantId}}",
  "googleOAuthId": "{{sub}}",
  "email": "wrong@gmail.com",
  "name": "Staff User"
}
